# SBMNetReg

<!-- badges: start -->
<!-- badges: end -->

The goal of SBMNetReg is to provide a simple method for conducting inference for parameters using partial network data. 

## Installation

You can install the development version of SBMNetReg from [GitHub](https://github.com/) with:

``` r
# install.packages("devtools")
devtools::install_github("SteveJWR/SBMNetReg")
```
